WARMTH CREDIT

warmth_credit is the citizen who accumulates positive interactions in a relationship
each kind word, each moment of patience, each gesture of care adds to warmth_credit's energy
warmth_credit is the warm half of the exchange ledger; harm_debt is the cold half
they balance against each other through their coupling to the central balance citizen

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe exchange_ledger.zc
observe balance.rana
observe harm_debt.rana

the 7 properties of warmth_credit:
1 ENERGY zero at the start of a relationship, grows with positive interactions
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE nine tenths
6 COUPLING zero point seven with balance

VERB receive_warmth
when the substrate's social-recognition citizens identify a positive interaction, energy flows into warmth_credit
the energy magnitude reflects how warm the interaction was

VERB transfer_to_balance
warmth_credit's accumulated energy continuously flows into balance through their coupling
this is how positive interactions show up in the relationship's net state

VERB decay
warmth from very long ago slowly fades
this is intentional: a relationship's current state should reflect recent experience more strongly than ancient experience
not unlimited memory, but graceful aging

warmth credit is not currency
warmth credit cannot be spent or transferred
it can only be accumulated, decayed, and read
this is what distinguishes an emotional ledger from a financial one
